{"tid":1240962,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"父母由藍絲變黃絲經驗分享","createTime":"2019-06-18T13:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T13:57:50.000Z","uid":182195,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"97754fbb9133d4829e74bb5d0a5ac3a65460e936","tid":1240962,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:57:50.000Z","msg":"今日見到有人開post教人CUT CCTVB<br />\n我有感而發想分享少少<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於我呀哥係IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企所有關於網絡野、電腦問題，甚至電器（老一輩覺得呢啲都關IT狗事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）嘅野都係佢搞<br />\n<br />\n然而，食住呢個優勢<br />\n四年前呀哥已經係屋企裝咗NOW TV電視盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教埋老豆老母點開黎睇<br />\n兩年前趁住要換電視機cut埋cctvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆老母從此只能睇到NOW新聞台<br />\n最初都屌哂鬼<br />\n但佢地根本唔知點樣先睇得返CCTVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後慢慢習慣就已經冇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家屋企人一齊食飯時都係睇NOW新聞<br />\n<br />\n最近發生咁多事<br />\n雖然老豆老母仍然唔肯陪我一齊上街<br />\n但至少都係同聲同條一齊屌林鄭同警察<br />\n出街飲茶又會幫手同啲茶客講道理<br />\n仲唔會反對我上街，好支持我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">希望各位真係狠心啲CUT咗CCTVB</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心有用"}]}